high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left at the window to reach the sink.
Grab the black plate from the sink.
Turn around, then turn left when you get to the fridge.
Cool the plate in the fridge, then take it out again.
Turn left and walk back to the sink.
Place the plate in the cabinet underneath the sink, to the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled plate in a cabinet.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the sink.
Take the black plate out of the sink basin.
Turn around and start walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the black plate inside on the top shelf, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the plate then close the door again.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the right in front of you and place the chilled plate in the cabinet then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled black plate in a kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the blue trash can then turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the black plate in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge, then pick up the plate from the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk to right cabinet below the sink.
Place the plate in the right cabinet below the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled black plate in the right cabinet below the sink.
